            <li><a href="https://port-0-cpaservice-dc9c2nlss8snjp.sel5.cloudtype.app/login">로그인</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://port-0-cpaservice-dc9c2nlss8snjp.sel5.cloudtype.app/register">회원가입</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>


    <div id="main_header">
        <p>화장품 검색</p>
